8434159b-52a9-493d-900a-25e797fdd31a	95d3a015-2047-462d-ac88-feffd47950ef	WRQ-CUST-253E	480f3e36-bf9a-4794-8358-bfd32817072e	Dear John Doe,\n\nWe have initiated the SEO update task for your Homepage page title. Our team conducted a comprehensive review of your CMS structure and existing documents to locate the Homepage and implement the requested changes.\n\nThe objective is to update your Homepage page title to "Shop with us | LuXORA" to enhance your search engine visibility and browser tab display. We have completed the initial assessment phase and reviewed all available document types within your system.\n\nThe next steps involve finalizing the page title update and conducting quality assurance testing to confirm the changes render correctly across search engine previews and browser tabs.\n\nWe will provide you with a completion update shortly.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]	\N	\N	DRAFT	\N	2026-06-15 07:31:35.591828+00
2d89f08e-f156-4fe4-ae3c-8211819ccb96	9a2ca280-c4e3-4e0a-af45-4b23307181d1	WRQ-CUST-253E	d73f3432-c63c-4cc9-bcb2-1b276cd96177	Dear John Doe,\n\nWe are pleased to inform you that the Home page title update for your LUXORA storefront has been completed successfully.\n\nOur team conducted a comprehensive review of your CMS and determined that a Home page document did not previously exist. Accordingly, we created a new Home page with the SEO title "Shop with us | LUXORA," as requested. The page has been configured with the appropriate metadata and slug to ensure optimal search engine visibility and user experience.\n\nThe page title will now display correctly in browser tabs and search engine preview results. This update supports your SEO objectives and enhances your site's discoverability.\n\nShould you require any further adjustments or have questions regarding this implementation, please do not hesitate to contact us.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Team]	\N	\N	DRAFT	\N	2026-06-15 07:47:02.004861+00
